content.rendered:
Directed by Sabir Khan

Written by Sabir Khan. Venu Sriram. Sanamjit Singh Talwar

Star Abhimanyu Dasani. Imam Hossain Saju(Playback Singer). Shirley Setia. Samir Soni(Brother). Mukesh Agrohari(Don). Shaan Kakkar(Gangster). Sammratt Kapoor(Darshi). Naren Kumar. Rohit Kumar(Omi). Shyam Lal(Babloo). Jay Parashar(Inspector Roy cop). Shilpa Shetty Kundra. Samar Shukla(Singh). Palak Singh

Language Hindi

Producers Arun Singh Dikky. Siraj Kasmani. Ayaz Khan. Farhan Khan. Sheel Nimbalkar. Ajay Ashok Singh. Roshan Singh

Production Sony Pictures Networks Productions .Sabbir Khan Films .Sony Pictures Releasing
